Teachers that are currently using personal email accounts will need to contact support@markbookapp.com to request existing class data transfers, if required.  For TVDSB Users 09 Sep 2022 01:00:00 -0400 https://www.markbook.com News On Tuesday, September 6th, Single Sign On (SSO) was implemented for TVDSB MarkBook (Cloud) users. Teachers are now required to sign onto MarkBook using their TVDSB e-mail address and password in the Microsoft 365 Apps environment. Please follow the Information Guidesheet for "Transfer from Individual to Corporate Domain using SSO in MarkBook®”. Teachers that are already signing onto MarkBook with their TVDSB email address will have their existing class data maintained.
